|WKBIntelligence:                Range: |YKB1-200
 
    |YKOIntelligence is similar to what is currently known as intelligence
quotient, but also includes mnemonic ability, reasoning, and learning
ability outside those measured by any written test. In melee combat,
more intelligent characters are able to better use their equipment, and
discern their enemies' weaknesses, leading to greater success at hitting
their enemies, and also in deflecting incoming blows using their armor.
Intelligence is essential for guilds that make heavy use of mental powers
to manipulate the world directly, or indirectly through arcane spells.
